Package com.stormpath.shiro.authz

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PermissionsEditor
    A PermissionsEditor allows one to read and manipulate (append or remove) permissions on an underlying data structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomDataPermissionsEditor
    A CustomDataPermissionsEditor can read or modify a collection of Shiro permission Strings stored in a CustomData resource.
